OL,6,FJersey's government has confirmed the
OL,7,Fcurrent tenants of the Havre de Pas
OL,8,FLido will be able to remain until next
OL,9,Fyear.
OL,11,FIt follows a demonstration in the
OL,12,FRoyal Square on Wednesday (23 October)
OL,13,Fover plans to evict Marcus Calvani
OL,14,Fbefore the completion of a tender
OL,15,Fprocess to find a potential new
OL,16,Foperator.
OL,18,FMr Calvani told ITV News that the saga
OL,19,Fhas taken a huge toll on his mental
OL,20,Fhealth.
