OL,6,FHe said: "It's affecting my parents
OL,7,Fand my family and most importantly our
OL,8,Fstaff who are at a breaking point of
OL,9,Fanxiety and some of them will be faced
OL,10,Fwith losing their homes."
OL,12,FHis appeal to stay was backed by
OL,13,FDeputy David Warr, who intended for
OL,14,Fthe matter to be debated by
OL,15,Fpoliticians in the States, before
OL,16,Fwithdrawing his proposition following
OL,17,Fdiscussions with ministers.
