OL,6,FIn a statement from Constable Simon
OL,7,FCrowcroft, Assistant Minister for
OL,8,FInfrastructure, announced: "Following
OL,9,Fproductive discussions with Deputy
OL,10,FDavid Warr, we can confirm that the
OL,11,Fcurrent occupier will be able to
OL,12,Fremain on-site until the end of 2025.
OL,14,F"As part of this arrangement, the
OL,15,Foccupier will be required to sign a
OL,16,Fformal contract and cover rent and a
OL,17,Fportion of utility bills from the end
OL,18,Fof October. A tender process for the
OL,19,Ffuture operation of the Lido will
OL,20,Fproceed as planned.
